{"tid":1803292,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥迪奧拿：為2020/21準備！","createTime":"2019-12-30T06:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T09:30:35.000Z","uid":31626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"664b0246d5183abd3eca07e85577371c8e97ef71","tid":1803292,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】曼城主帥哥迪奧拿從不愛修飾，他說已放眼來季，餘下球季的每一仗，都是為來季東山再起好準備。<br />\n<br />\n曼城於周日以2:0打敗錫菲聯，那是哥迪奧拿領軍以來第100場聯賽勝仗，然而才不過半季，藍月目前只能排在第3位，與榜首利物浦足足有14分的分差。當被問到如何在下半季追趕利物浦時，再一次，哥帥坦言衛冕無望。<br />\n<br />\n「不！想及那事情是不切實際。擁有如此數字的利物浦，為何還去想（追趕）？現在只是準備做得好，儘量追貼榜首、為盃賽作準備，以及為來季而戰。」<br />\n<br />\n「每一場比賽都有助我們加以改善，為來季作準備，但願我們可以做得更好。現在我們有3天時間休戰，感謝有3天時間去復元，備戰下仗對愛華頓。那是你必須去做的事情。」"},{"pid":"da84d113e2e39c85fe2f88a3b673c4a3ee73fbd6","tid":1803292,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:04:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkbJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=2138274a\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"24fd3321a3fb2a6f9480f0bd68f57077f09e6326","tid":1803292,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d764c3e14b78069f804bbb31f5369c7c63e884","tid":1803292,"uid":1065,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"見到&quot;不！&quot; 以為係nineup報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1207ffcdb3319c9a4462b86561b870d936f2803","tid":1803292,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"